    {
      "title": "Programmation Chauffe-eau cuisine",
      "path": "programmation_cuisine",
      "subview": true,
      "icon": "mdi:calendar-clock",
      "cards": [
        {
          "type": "tile",
          "entity": "switch.chauffe_eau_cuisine",
          "name": "Chauffe-eau cuisine",
          "icon": "mdi:water-boiler",
          "color": "orange",
          "features": [
            {
              "type": "toggle"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "conditional",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "condition": "state",
              "entity": "switch.chauffe_eau_cuisine",
              "state": "on"
            }
          ],
          "card": {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "{% set dt = now() - states.switch.chauffe_eau_cuisine.last_changed %}\n{% set h = (dt.seconds // 3600) | int %}\n{% set m = ((dt.seconds % 3600) // 60) | int %}\n{% if h > 0 %}🕐 Actif depuis **{{ h }}h {{ m }} min**{% else %}🕐 Actif depuis **{{ m }} min**{% endif %}\n\n{% set wh_now = states('sensor.chauffe_eau_cuisine') | float(0) %}\n{% set wh_start = states('input_number.chauffe_eau_cuisine_wh_debut_de_cycle') | float(0) %}\n{% set delta = [wh_now - wh_start, 0] | max | round(0) | int %}\n⚡ **{% if delta >= 1000 %}{{ (delta / 1000) | round(2) }} kWh{% else %}{{ delta }} Wh{% endif %}** consommés ce cycle"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "custom:scheduler-card",
          "include": [
            "switch.chauffe_eau_cuisine"
          ],
          "title": "📅 Programmation hebdomadaire",
          "show_header_toggle": false
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "### ⏱ Minuterie\n\nÉtat : **{% if is_state('timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine', 'active') %}🟢 En cours{% else %}⏸ Arrêtée{% endif %}**{% if state_attr('timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine', 'finishes_at') %} — termine à **{{ as_timestamp(state_attr('timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine', 'finishes_at')) | timestamp_custom('%H:%M:%S') }}**{% endif %}"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal-stack",
          "cards": [
            {
              "type": "button",
              "show_icon": false,
              "name": "15 min",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "timer.start",
                "service_data": {
                  "entity_id": "timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine",
                  "duration": "00:15:00"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "show_icon": false,
              "name": "30 min",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "timer.start",
                "service_data": {
                  "entity_id": "timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine",
                  "duration": "00:30:00"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "show_icon": false,
              "name": "1 h",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "timer.start",
                "service_data": {
                  "entity_id": "timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine",
                  "duration": "01:00:00"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "show_icon": false,
              "name": "2 h",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "timer.start",
                "service_data": {
                  "entity_id": "timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine",
                  "duration": "02:00:00"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "show_icon": false,
              "name": "4 h",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "timer.start",
                "service_data": {
                  "entity_id": "timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine",
                  "duration": "04:00:00"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "entities",
          "title": "Durée custom",
          "entities": [
            {
              "entity": "input_number.duree_custom_chauffe_eau_cuisine",
              "name": "Durée"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal-stack",
          "cards": [
            {
              "type": "button",
              "name": "Lancer minuterie",
              "icon": "mdi:play",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "script.lancer_minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "name": "Annuler",
              "icon": "mdi:stop",
              "tap_action": {
                "action": "call-service",
                "service": "timer.cancel",
                "service_data": {
                  "entity_id": "timer.minuterie_chauffe_eau_cuisine"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
